initd -- simple dependency based init system


Library Dependencies:

* boost >=1.49

Build:

~/d/initd$ mkdir build
~/d/initd$ cd build
~/d/initd/build$ cmake ..
~/d/initd/build$ make

Run:

~/d/initd/build$ cd init
~/d/initd/build/init$ ./init ../../demo.conf

Press ^C to stop initd.

For config example see demo.conf.
